New Nonstop Alaska Airlines Jet Service
Between Orange County & Oakland.
• Now you can fly between Orange County and Oakland
25 minutes faster! Three jet flights depart every business day.
Experience The Comforts Our Board Rooms.
• Alaska Airlines' exclusive airport club rooms are conveniently
located in San Francisco, Los Angeles*, Portland, Seattle and
Anchorage. Call 1-800-654-5669 or stop by any Board Room
for membership information.
*Board Room members may use TWA's Ambassador Club in Los Angeles.
New Jet Service Between
Anchorage & Dutch Harbor Begins April 4.
• This new Alaska Airlines service will compliment flights
currently operated by PenAir and Reeve Aleutian Airways.
Plan Your Sunshine Vacation Now!
• Alaska Airlines flies to Mazatlan, Puerto Vallarta, Los Cabos,
and Guadalajara, Mexico; and Palm Springs, San Diego,
Phoenix and Tucson.
Call Your Travel Agent or Alaska Airlines Vacations at
1-800-468-2248 for information on the following vacations:
• Mexico Vacations
• California Vacations: Disneyland® Park,
Knott's Berry Farm, Universal Studios, San Francisco,
Napa Valley & San Diego
• The Far East: Russia & China
• Alaska Summer Vacations
